# Clean product URLs: /memorials/<slug> serves memorial.html.
#
# Do NOT add a `/memorial -> /memorials` redirect here: Cloudflare Pages
# canonicalises rewrite targets by stripping `.html` (so `/memorial.html`
# resolves as `/memorial`), which would then match that rule and bounce
# every product page back to the listing. memorial.html itself handles the
# "no slug" case gracefully, so a bare `/memorial` visit is harmless.
/memorials/:slug   /memorial.html   200
